WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.920
Step-by-step guide for self-assisted DGTRAID account opening.

00:03.920 --> 00:11.680
Open our website www.integratedindia.in and click here to open your free DGTRAID account with us.

00:11.680 --> 00:18.080
Enter your PAN details. Enter the OTP. Allow to fetch the KYC documents through Digilocco.

00:18.080 --> 00:23.360
Capture your selfie photo. Draw your signature on screen or upload your web signature.

00:23.360 --> 00:26.640
Enter your PAN details. Enter the personal details.

00:26.640 --> 00:30.720
Confirm the trading preferences. Select the choice of nomination.

00:30.720 --> 00:34.160
Check the details before proceeding with the E-Sign process.

00:34.160 --> 00:36.480
Submit the term insurance preference.

00:36.480 --> 00:39.440
Click sign the document to do the E-Sign process.

00:39.440 --> 00:42.640
Enter the art hard number. Enter the OTP.

00:42.640 --> 00:44.800
Onwarding process successfully.

00:44.800 --> 00:46.800
Thank you for choosing Integrated.

